title: Sample Book, British Standard Exporter, 1928–29
description: Large cloth-bound book entitled "British Standard Exporter." Contains samples of textiles – cotton, wool, linen, and synthetics from various English centers and firms. Completely indexed. Illustrated with photographs and advertising material.

tombstone.epitaph: Sample Book, British Standard Exporter, 1928–29; England; paper, cotton, wool, linen; H x W: 30.8 × 26 cm (12 1/8 × 10 1/4 in.); 1966-65-1
